<plot>This film is about the documentary filmmaker 'Stiliyan Parushev' (qv), whose life is full of dramatic twists that have left marks on his works. His reminiscences take us back to the times of WWII and his participation in it, as well as to the early years of the Bulgarian cinema. Stiliyan Parushev shot about 300 documentaries, from "Tiger Beetle" in 1952 to "Boarding House For Homeless Dogs" in 1992.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?018711</url></doc>
